    "4111301": {
        "Desc": "Chat with Mona about the meteorites and scrying",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hi Mona! Thanks to you, we've managed to get rid of loads and loads of meteorites!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "Ah, good timing! There's something I need you to do."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "Remember how I was saying that the meteorites belonged to someone's constellation?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "Theoretically, it's not possible for stars that are goodness knows how many light-years away to suddenly turn into meteors and fall out of the sky. But, however paradoxical it may be, this is the reality."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "If we want to get to the bottom of this, the best way is to find out whose constellation it was."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "Based on what you've told me, it seems that all victims of the meteorites fell into a deep sleep, and all of them dreamed of a snowy mountain."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "Now, we may not know which mountain this was — but we can safely assume that it's not Dragonspine. Otherwise, someone would have recognized it, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "Did everyone definitely have the same dream? And where exactly were they in the dream? These are the questions that we need answers to."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "I need you to find out more details about the sleepers' dreams. The more information we have, the closer we can get to the truth."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Seems we should head somewhere with lots of people around."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "That way, we should be able to find more victims to question."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "I need to stay in an undisturbed environment. So, I will leave the investigating to you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Is there anywhere that we haven't been to yet?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Oz",
                    "T": "There is <color=#00E1FFFF>Qingce Village</color>, in Liyue... Although, it does not usually match your suggestion of \"somewhere with lots of people around.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Oz",
                    "T": "That said, I suspect that the Millelith will have turned that area into a site where victims can receive medical attention, much as they did at Wangshu Inn."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
