    "4111315": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Gao the Sixth",
                    "T": "Phwoar! That's brought me back from the brink, that has!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Did you have a dream while you were sleeping?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gao the Sixth",
                    "T": "Only the most exhausting dream of my whole life!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Really? Why, what happened?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Were you on a mountain?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gao the Sixth",
                    "T": "Yes... how did you know? Way up in the mountains, the highest mountain I've ever seen... It was freezing up there."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Were you outside in the snow?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gao the Sixth",
                    "T": "Well, sort of. Up a snowy mountain, to be precise. It was huge, and it was freezing cold... The moment I fell asleep, I was standing at the foot of the mountain."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What were you doing there?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gao the Sixth",
                    "T": "I'm not sure. It's like I was... possessed. I was consumed by the idea of climbing up the mountain and trying to reach the summit."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Was there something special at the summit, or?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gao the Sixth",
                    "T": "Who knows? Honestly, it's like I became a completely different person in my dream. Don't ask me why, I have no idea..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "So it wasn't \"you\" who wanted to climb the mountain?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gao the Sixth",
                    "T": "It's hard to describe... It's like I was being controlled, as if somebody else put the idea of climbing the mountain into my head. I know how crazy that sounds, but..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fischl",
                    "T": "An intruder trespassed in the dark recesses of your soul!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Oz",
                    "T": "An idea not autonomously generated by the individual, but that appeared within the subconscious... Yes, the signs do indeed point towards mind control."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I should be used to this by now, but..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "The things you two say are not even remotely similar..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "All the other victims we've met have talked about being cold, and needing to rest... Were they all climbing the mountain, too?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "How can they all be having the same dream?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon doesn't even wanna think about it... We need to update <color=#00E1FFFF>Mona</color> on all of this!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "4111307": {
        "Desc": "Tell Mona about the meteorites",
        "Step": "Apart from the spate of unconsciousness caused by the meteorites, the appearance of the Fatui has also aroused your suspicions. Fortunately, the arrival of the astrologist Mona has given your efforts a much-needed boost. With the help of her mystical scrying techniques, you begin to delve into these mysteries...",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Mona, we found some stuff out!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fischl",
                    "T": "An ice-capped mountain looms over the world from far above the clouds... That is the place from which this burgeoning darkness proceeds."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "Ice-capped mountain? Is that all?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It is the same ice-capped mountain in everyone's dream."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "It's a really really high mountain that no one's ever seen before, and it's super cold up there. The sleepers are forced to try and climb to the summit, but they don't know why."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "Climb the mountain? To the summit?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "What sort of person would wish to reach the summit of that mountain? And how is their desire strong enough to exert an influence on others?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fischl",
                    "T": "Perchance some poor soul lies there, buried in the snow, hounded to death on the mountain?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Oz",
                    "T": "Or... Some intrepid explorer was exceptionally keen to conquer that particular mountain."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "I'll do another reading!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "Aha! I see something here... It's a little vague but I think I can get his name... Ah, yes! <color=#00E1FFFF>\"Leonard\"</color>!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wow, that was fast!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "Well, in case you'd forgotten... I am a genius!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "\"Leonard...\" Paimon's never heard that name before."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
