    "4111308": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "Any junior fortune-teller could have told you this, but... That man was a Fatui Harbinger! That was too close, how did you manage to get caught up with a guy like him?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Oz",
                    "T": "A Fatui Harbinger? Why, their wickedness knows no bounds!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "A Harbinger? Goodness..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "Whatever he was planning to do... He was heading straight for you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "And he is an extremely powerful individual! I sensed it the moment I looked at him. He's far more powerful than you'd imagine."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "As much as it pains me to admit it..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Oz",
                    "T": "Surely his power cannot match that of the astrological genius of the century?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "I never said that...! His strength may exceed mine by a hair's breadth... But in astrology alone, he doesn't come close!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "This reminds Paimon of something... We ran into some Fatui at Wangshu Inn, too!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What interest could the Fatui have in the meteorites?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "They must be plotting something."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "Hmm... Maybe, just maybe..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh! The Fatui are the ones who caused the meteor shower in the first place! Was that it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "Paimon, that was my line! Get your own!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Sorry... Paimon's mouth just works so much faster than everyone else's."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Does the power to summon a meteorite strike really exist?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah... Where'd they get the power to pull stars out of the sky!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fischl",
                    "T": "Ozvaldo Hrafnavins, what is thy opinion?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Oz",
                    "T": "I think that anything is possible, mein Fräulein."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fischl",
                    "T": "So long as they can afford to pay the price, they will never stop sowing their seeds of destruction across the land... Fatui, your sins shall not go unremembered."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Oz",
                    "T": "I also believe that miracles can happen."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fischl",
                    "T": "Astral emissary, you have performed admirably as a member of my retinue. I will dispatch my forces to protect you, and they will ensure that the encroaching darkness shall bring you no harm."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Oz",
                    "T": "She means me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "No need! Paimon thinks that our current lineup works just fine... No need to fix it if it ain't broke!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "You underestimate me, Fischl! I'm far stronger than you seem to think."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Oz",
                    "T": "Mein Fräulein trusts no one more than yourself, my lady, she is simply concerned for your well-being."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "There's really no need. In any case, you're in a much more perilous position than I am. If anything, you need my protection."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Mona, you're a good person."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "...Huh? Wh—What're you saying that for?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Fischl, you're a good person."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Fischl",
                    "T": "Naturally!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Mona",
                    "T": "For now, we must deal with the new threat. My astrolabe tells me that a new meteorite has landed, and it's the <color=#00E1FFFF>biggest one yet</color>."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
